":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"code":"[0, 4]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"left","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text"